shape: sequence_diagram

# Define participants
User: User
Frontend: Web Frontend (TypeScript)
DB: Database

# Scenario: User Registration
User -> Frontend: Provide registration details
Frontend -> DB: Persist user information
DB -> Frontend: Success confirmation
Frontend -> User: Registration successful

# Scenario: History Consultation
User -> Frontend: Request participation history
Frontend -> DB: Query game history and statistics
DB -> Frontend: Return raw game data
Frontend -> Frontend: Calculate metrics (win/loss ratio, etc.)
Frontend -> User: Display history and metrics